[Xuantian House]

42
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:55,220
Move it here.

43
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:01,540
Careful.

44
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:05,940
[Tianze Hall]

45
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:06,580
Carry them to the back.

46
00:04:06,580 --> 00:04:07,940
Higher.

47
00:04:07,940 --> 00:04:09,020
Yes. That's it.

48
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:10,620
Bring them to the main chamber.

49
00:04:10,620 --> 00:04:11,100
Yes.

50
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:11,700
All right.

51
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:15,420
Didn't you follow Master Ling

52
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:16,740
to pick out the wedding gown?

53
00:04:16,820 --> 00:04:18,220
Why are you back so soon?

54
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:19,340
I didn't.

55
00:04:19,340 --> 00:04:20,780
I haven't seen her yet.

56
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:22,180
Yesterday, Master Ling said

57
00:04:22,180 --> 00:04:23,420
she would take Yingshi

58
00:04:23,420 --> 00:04:24,900
to visit Madam's tomb today.

59
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:26,260
I guess

60
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:27,660
they left early this morning.

61
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:28,420
Knowing they have been

62
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:30,060
inseparable these days,

63
00:04:30,060 --> 00:04:31,700
they will probably return at midnight.

64
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:35,580
As I have observed these days,

65
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:36,780
Yingshi

66
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:39,260
is a trustworthy man.

67
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:40,940
Master Ling and him

68
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:43,300
are finally together.

69
00:04:43,540 --> 00:04:45,420
I won't feel sorry

70
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,100
to face Madam

71
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:49,380
after I die.

72
00:04:54,820 --> 00:04:55,340
Madam.

73
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:56,940
These are for the wedding.

74
00:04:57,900 --> 00:04:58,900
This red rope...

75
00:04:58,900 --> 00:04:59,500
Let go.

76
00:05:00,020 --> 00:05:01,300
So beautiful.

77
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,780
I want to make it into clothes

78
00:05:02,780 --> 00:05:04,140
and wrap it around me.

79
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:05,140
I'm sure

80
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:07,500
Master Ling will like it.

81
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:09,620
Is it nice?

82
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:10,580
Yes.

83
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:13,940
I'm sure Master Ling will like this.

84
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:15,180
She has been mad for days.

85
00:05:15,300 --> 00:05:16,060
He will like me for sure.

86
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,140
Second Young Master

87
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:18,660
begged Master Ling to spare her life.

88
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:21,260
And she has ended up in this state.

89
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:23,260
No evil deed goes unpunished.

90
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:25,220
She had it coming.

91
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:30,260
Madam.

92
00:05:30,260 --> 00:05:31,420
Come here.

93
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:32,460
Madam, don't run.

94
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:33,300
Madam.

95
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:34,180
Be careful.

96
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:35,380
So beautiful!

97
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:36,140
Madam.

98
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:41,820
Madam.

99
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:45,300
Do I look pretty?

100
00:05:45,740 --> 00:05:46,380
Madam.

101
00:05:46,380 --> 00:05:47,780
Please head back with me.

102
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:48,820
Do I look pretty?

103
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:49,340
Xiaoliu.

104
00:05:50,060 --> 00:05:50,620
Come here.

105
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:51,980
Young Master wants to ask you something.

106
00:05:58,940 --> 00:06:00,260
Greetings, Young Master.

107
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:04,500
Didn't I ask you
to keep an eye on Mother

108
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:06,660
and not to let her wander around?

109
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,620
Where did she get the red cloth from?

110
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:12,420
Um...

111
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,020
Answer Young Master.

112
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:16,620
Why are you hesitating?
Do you have a death wish.

113
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:19,180
Please forgive me, Young Master.

114
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:21,380
It's my fault
for not watching Madam closely.

115
00:06:21,740 --> 00:06:23,260
Madam took the red cloth

116
00:06:23,780 --> 00:06:25,740
from the main hall.

117
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:27,700
Main hall?

118
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:29,140
You restricted everyone

119
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:30,820
from leaving Cangyu Abode.

120
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:32,020
I only found out this morning

121
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:33,740
when I chased after Madam

122
00:06:34,820 --> 00:06:35,620
that Master Ling

123
00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:37,780
and Mr. Yingshi of the Shadow Sect
are about to get married.

124
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:40,100
The wedding
is on the fifteenth of this month.

125
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:44,220
Leave.

126
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:45,740
Yes.

127
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:58,370
[Xuantian House]

128
00:07:15,980 --> 00:07:17,020
What are you doing here?

129
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:21,740
I came here to demand an explanation.

130
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:23,580
You are getting married soon.

131
00:07:23,580 --> 00:07:24,540
How could you

132
00:07:24,780 --> 00:07:26,580
not inform me of such a big matter?

133
00:07:28,020 --> 00:07:29,420
I'm afraid I'm the last one
in the entire palace

134
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:31,980
to know about it.

135
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:34,860
I planned to tell you on the day.

136
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:37,460
Yingshi and I don't like trouble.

137
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:39,180
We want to spare ourselves from trouble

138
00:07:39,180 --> 00:07:39,980
on the wedding day.

139
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:43,940
Xuan.

140
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:45,740
Do you really want to marry Yingshi?

141
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:47,420
Of course.

142
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:49,460
Do you really like him?

143
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:58,300
He is a lowly

144
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:00,020
shadow guard.

145
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:01,820
He doesn't deserve you.

146
00:08:03,060 --> 00:08:04,460
I disagree with this marriage.

147
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:07,380
How funny.

148
00:08:08,260 --> 00:08:09,700
Do I even need

149
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:11,060
your approval?

150
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:12,260
Besides,

151
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:14,780
speaking of suitability,

152
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:17,580
Ling Yuanzheng and my mother

153
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:19,620
made a suitable pair of equal status.

154
00:08:19,860 --> 00:08:20,980
But look what had happened.

155
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:23,460
If you want to talk about
an unsuitable partner,

156
00:08:25,060 --> 00:08:26,020
consider

157
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:27,220
your dear mother.

158
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:36,380
Xuan, don't be mad.

159
00:08:36,740 --> 00:08:37,340
I'm too concerned

160
00:08:37,420 --> 00:08:38,980
and get anxious.

161
00:08:39,540 --> 00:08:41,380
Since you have made up your mind,

162
00:08:41,460 --> 00:08:43,300
of course I will support you.

163
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:45,780
According to the customs,

164
00:08:46,060 --> 00:08:48,260
the bride's feet
shouldn't touch the ground

165
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:49,860
until she gets into the sedan chair
after leaving her parents' house.

166
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:51,740
On the wedding day,

167
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:53,220
I will escort you.

168
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:15,220
[Cangyu Abode]

169
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,020
Young Master.

170
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:19,020
I made an excuse

171
00:09:19,020 --> 00:09:20,900
to go down the mountain with disciples
who purchase wedding items.

172
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,220
I brought back the letter
from the Medicine King Valley.

173
00:09:24,220 --> 00:09:25,700
They have figured out
Yingshi's identity.

174
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:26,460
Besides,

175
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:27,580
it writes

176
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:29,180
that the Medicine King Valley is ready.

177
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:30,940
They will assist you in taking over

178
00:09:30,940 --> 00:09:32,140
the position of the palace master
whenever you are ready.

179
00:09:34,220 --> 00:09:35,700
Send them a message back.

180
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:36,700
Tell Zhan Yuechi

181
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:38,620
that Xuan is about to get married,

182
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:40,340
he should hurry up and set off.

183
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:41,700
If he is late,

184
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:43,060
Xuan is going to marry the man

185
00:09:43,060 --> 00:09:44,620
he has hated for years.

186
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:46,140
I will see to it right away.

187
00:09:50,820 --> 00:09:52,300
Oh, Xuan.

188
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:54,620
Isn't it enough

189
00:09:54,940 --> 00:09:56,540
you have me by your side

190
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:58,340
in this mountain?

191
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:01,700
Why do you want to marry that man?

192
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:04,660
Why force me?

193
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,660
Why force my hand?

194
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:15,700
♪If hand waves are
the prelude to farewell♪

195
00:10:16,140 --> 00:10:19,300
♪If words hold no intention to stall♪

196
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:21,580
♪Goodbye♪

197
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:25,620
♪Should be reserved
for when our lives are at stake♪

198
00:10:26,890 --> 00:10:30,220
♪If time rushes swiftly
like wind and dust♪

199
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:33,940
♪If tears come before words
after waking up♪

200
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:36,620
♪May you not be drowned in bitterness♪

201
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:38,220
♪I only wish your eyes♪

202
00:10:38,380 --> 00:10:41,300
♪As pure as snow♪
